.</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> Those with mental health problems may have these exacerbated by isolation.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Communications (telephone, cellphone</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">, internet access, information</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">) may also </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">be lacking</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> or </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">of poor quality</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> in remote areas</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">, creating issues of </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">their</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> own, </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">and </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">with consequences for </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">access to </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">transportation services.</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">1.3</span><